ing this within a postcolonial framework. Empathic Vision will appeal to anyone interested in the role of culture in post-September 11 global politics.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aART / Subjects & Themes / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362500640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503625006423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503625006/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles